   <express_ref linkend="requirement_assignment:arm:Requirement_assignment_arm.Requirement_source.description"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Requirement_assignment_arm.Requirement_source.description">
the text that provides further information about the 
<b>Requirement_source</b>.
The value of this attribute need not be specified.
</ext_description>
